						<p>Incomplete. It registers a gift for a twilight lamp to the temple of Piṇakk[arukk*]um Nāyanār at Malaiyaḍikkuṟichchi, a southern hamlet of Śri Parāntakach-chaturvēḍimaṅgalam, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Āri-nāḍu by Nārāyaṉaṉ Mādhavaṉ, a native of a village in Purisaināḍu, a subdivision of Malai-maṇḍalam.</p>						

